This is a SvelteKit project with Tailwind CSS.

STYLING RULES:
- Use Tailwind CSS utility classes for ALL styling
- Do NOT use <style> blocks for layout/spacing — use Tailwind classes in markup
- Follow mobile-first responsive design (sm:, md:, lg: breakpoints)

SVELTEKIT WEBCONTAINER RULES:
- package.json MUST have "type": "module"
- Use vite.config.ts (TypeScript), NOT vite.config.js
- @sveltejs/kit/vite is ESM-only and fails with CJS require()
- svelte.config.js uses JS (standard convention)

IMPORTANT:
- Always run `npm install && npm run dev` to start
- Never use `svelte-kit dev` directly — always use `npm run dev`
